{"tid":2388000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"護苗基金遲來的譴責 只登官網無上載fb 網民斥鬼祟","createTime":"2021-01-30T18:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T01:30:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a8bd640e51d2fd80579471c8ee15337f6f02a4af","tid":2388000,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:18:30.000Z","msg":"反送中運動以來一直未有就警方侵犯兒童暴行發聲的慈善團體「護苗基金」，周五終於「開金口」，針對警員非禮六名女童案件發表聲明，稱對判刑感到失望，警員行為「天理不容」，惟公眾未有因這份聲明原諒基金。律政司稱會研究是否上訴。<br />\n<br />\n毒品調查科警員余俊鑫先後狎玩六名女童，被控非禮等八項罪名，上周三被判入獄46個月。由藝人蕭芳芳創立的護苗基金在周三及周四一直保持緘默，大批網民在基金的facebook專頁留言，質問：「警察性侵女童六名，貴會又裝聾扮啞？」<br />\n<br />\n基金促請法律改革委員會盡快落實《性罪行檢討中的判刑及相關事項》的建議條文，使新訂罪行刑罰更具阻嚇作用，令兒童得到更大的保護屏障。聲明未有促請律政司就判刑上訴。近年不斷就社運人士判刑「過輕」上訴的律政司則回覆稱，會研究法官的判刑理據和主控官的報告，然後決定是否需要跟進。<br />\n<br />\n護苗基金的聲明僅在其網站上刊登，fb專頁未有上載，僅着網民參考網站內的聲明，結果引來更多網民不滿，「點解唔順道將篇聲明放埋落facebook page？若果要咁鬼鬼祟祟私私縮縮，咁做乜仲要post份聲明上官網啫，貼份聲明喺你辦公室門外塊壁報板咪得囉」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210131/P6J5B7BJPJCGRNQOVR72GO423E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210131%2FP6J5B7BJPJCGRNQOVR72GO423E%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=7eb12643\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210131%2FP6J5B7BJPJCGRNQOVR72GO423E%2F&h=6ecd19dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210131/P6J5B7BJPJCGRNQOVR72GO423E/</a>"},{"pid":"5ea64ef996e7f90034b9eab404d9a4e2d250b372","tid":2388000,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:19:26.000Z","msg":"呢個真係垃圾基金"},{"pid":"8d0b5ca8da533ec8d9f6a64df456589a6b9cc627","tid":2388000,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:22:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081010f8ea0feabc3234d12282e746830c3d2b39","tid":2388000,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:45:17.000Z","msg":"冇水cap了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809a09a59709defb945c5a75991cdb15cfb5f8f1","tid":2388000,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c206b5f6e67c0bec7645f7b901d2d68cf3a32c","tid":2388000,"uid":56734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"執7佢"},{"pid":"1b80145c9f9f41a2e56b2d4e926a5701fb23e14e","tid":2388000,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾，蕭芳芳收皮食屎啦"},{"pid":"4a73c5b56160884944e88d8812490f514c9dcc30","tid":2388000,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"改名做拜登基金算啦"},{"pid":"0b5b54dec880ad2cf416226dc9309116c13e6f7e","tid":2388000,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:30:00.000Z","msg":"個基金咁等錢洗， 搵啲細路女出嚟做咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}